Theme build instructions
========================

Option 1: just build the theme
------------------------------

In this directory just run ./build.sh
After successful build the theme file with '.edj' extension will be created
in this directory.


Option 2: build an rpm package
------------------------------

In this directory just run ./rpmbuild.sh
After successful build the '.src.rpm' and '.noarch.rpm' files will be created
in 'build/SRPMS' and 'build/RPMS' respectively.


Option 3: build a deb package
-----------------------------

In this directory just run ./debbuild.sh
After successful build the '.deb' file will be created in the current
directory.
